After Create an Streamlit app save it to <appname>.py then use the code below.

#Install localtunnel
!npm install localtunnel

#This will give you a IP address and a link.
!streamlit run app.py &>/content/logs.txt & npx localtunnel --port 8501 & curl ipv4.icanhazip.com

Copy the IP address and paste it to the following field given by the link, Boom !
